00:00:00.290 --> 00:00:05.160
And that's the primary goal of
contemporary health informatics,

00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:10.880
to turn our fragmented,
poorly coordinated health care system

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:16.280
into a system that uses digital
information in a seamless way to provide

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:22.250
optimal care to all patients,
even those as complicated as Marla.

00:00:23.430 --> 00:00:28.020
To understand that in more detail,
in Lesson 3 we'll go with

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:33.020
Marla as she visits her endocrinologist,
her diabetes doctor, Doctor Johnson.

